channel.title: Help! owners spawn in different areas
channel.description: Hi, im using the InsidiaX source and client and when I die, as an OWNER, I respawn in a different spot than where I have it set in the config.java. but as a normal player I spawn where I have it set. This to me is really strange and I have searched about the files trying to figure out why this is and I just can't find it. if anyone can help me it would be of my greatest appreciation.

item.title: Help! owners spawn in different areas
item.dc:creator: @Josh9 -Josh
item.description:
@Josh9 wrote:

Well i mean. if normal players spawn there, i doubt your everyday owner is going to be dieing alot. So just get used to typing ::tele XXXX YYYY to those coords after you die.
